vaanam ( english : vaanam ) is a 1988 indian tamil-language crime drama film directed by krish and produced by m. s. ramesh . the film stars silambarasan and bharath gopi in the lead roles . the film was produced by ramesh aravind and directed by krish . the film stars silambarasan and anushka shetty in the lead roles and music composed by yuvan shankar raja . the film was remade in hindi as vaanam &lt;unk&gt; .